Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:51.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&H4491F8&\blur3.333\bord1.333\t(1100,1101,\3c&H575656&)}それでまた歩いていけること　教わったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:06.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}神様　どうか　どうか　声を聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:09.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}ほんのちょっとでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:15.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}もう二度と　離れないように　あなたと二人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:18.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}あの星座のように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}結んでほしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:17.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&H575656&\blur3.333\bord0.667}你的手指 胸口 雙瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:27.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&H575656&\blur3.333\bord0.667}這樣炫目 在某些夜裡讓我有點眩暈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&H44CB2E&\blur3.333\bord0.667}那是不經意間落下來的 無比溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:37.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&H44CB2E&\blur3.333\bord0.667}被我吞入體內的 七彩的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:43.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&H4491F8&\blur3.333\bord1.333}就像迸開的火花 讓我很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:51.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\3c&H4491F8&\blur3.333\bord1.333\t(1100,1101,\3c&H575656&)}即使如此也能繼續前進 讓我學會了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:06.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}神啊 請你務必 務必讓我聽聽你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:09.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}一點點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:15.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}不要再次分離 和你兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:18.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}像那星座一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:22.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\blur3.333\bord1.333}繫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這能省下多少天的食費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為正月有點太奢侈了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是最近要節儉些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣明天開始又能吃好吃的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天大家都吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些剩下的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋澆飯 超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零 今天和小桃一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 就這樣吧 反正明天是週六
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 一起睡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次有一場 我無論如何都不想輸的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不回去學習不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習 你有考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己有多努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給對手 還有自己看的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定要和小零說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零說他有考試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 那麼這個時候該說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說「加油」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\fad(2000,0)\pos(174,298)}黑之河 ②
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後 在將棋會館裡見過桐山一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真的找著棋譜 然後列印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來想上去搭話的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看見他那嚴肅的表情還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山收集的棋譜是 島田8段和後藤9段的棋譜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那個可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽 那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不考慮我會贏的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且後來連島田的也不看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副一定會和後藤對局的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為自己是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒有想過 打倒後藤然後和島田對局的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 那就是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山希望的 並非是單方面的一廂情願
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是職業棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論被認同或是無視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在內心的某處測度自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堪稱殘忍的明白自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為能測度出才能稱為職業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那種知道自己也許能贏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是在比賽中有獲勝可能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊敗後藤再與島田先生決戰的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是 這樣的情況罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這樣卑劣的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是想要一點點接近勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是身為職業棋士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後藤的布局是「居飛車」「穴熊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對的我是「風車」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果後藤是厚重堅實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是輕鬆廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和後藤的交手已經是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次因為後藤厚重的包圍戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做好了持久戰的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並想將玉將更厚實地保護起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但穿上不習慣的甲胃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而扼殺了自己輕盈的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果一敗塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我吸取經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究了許多對策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定這次用我拿手的風格迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再固守玉將
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速靈活出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷造成小傷口來奪走對手的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對的後藤他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然穩健防守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耐心等待致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被他發動那一擊的話 我就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能有一絲的鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不也做到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百分百注定勝負的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在職業棋士眼中是絕對沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 快下雨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 天氣預報說今晚可能下雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪會這麼冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底有多少體力吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管受多少傷害都不會損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無機可趁…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流了這麼多血卻連眼皮都不眨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此 我的進攻也被限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一擊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棄飛車吃銀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這男人看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被巨大的力量衝擊 被掰開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑的水突然就全湧了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間我就被吸了下去 直至水底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很輕靈吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 還是有點沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2六角之後以5二金作防守了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果走6三金的話就好了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那步讓你的沉重暴露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身輕如燕是你的信條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束手無策 完全失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連靈魂都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是組合拳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種厚重深沉男子的樣子算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他多大了嘛 41？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過10年我能有嗎 那種魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很受女孩歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 總覺得超不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 總而言之今天去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選項A 扔進了就去姐姐的店裡喝幾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選項B 扔不進就回家抱被子汪汪哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是選項C？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs40\pos(348,304)}把貓撿回家照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫了別叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調整一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1098,712)}黑之河   ②
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠻有精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣一直贏下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對上你也是遲早的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起赤手空拳對打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對局一定更有趣才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些話想讓你轉告幸田的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關於那個跟蹤狂女兒的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說「請讓她快點住手」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得很困擾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(168,294)}門的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前首先要度過今天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天贏不了的話什麼都無從談起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田開八段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A級在位5年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對比看了很多棋譜 還真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出他的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅長的也好 弱點也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有能掌握他特點的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前沒跟他對局過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學時 在兒童將棋大會中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過他來當講師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常瘦弱 個子很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話十分文靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那時晉級了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在遠處看著他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以沒留下多少印象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說是「求勝將棋」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說是追求「不輸將棋」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這種類型的棋士對局時間會很長吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦煩躁起來就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被對方死咬不放的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛從後藤那裡收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在這裡輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對局是我先手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了雙矢倉圍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前為止和預想一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5二飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算全部正面抵擋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金後退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算讓飛車繞開嗎 那我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊緊圍好玉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該是在進攻的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候變成防守了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局面什麼時候變得這麼差了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失誤…應該沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局面會這麼嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻的手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於看我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了 小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你沒對局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 師兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退燒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你額頭還很燙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多注意身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是關係著你能否升級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是保證過不會勉強自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我還有師父保證
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才答應你不把那件事說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我馬上回去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一見面就責怪你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你突然來了 有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢…怎麼了 小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有什麼話想跟我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 其實師兄…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望師兄你能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給桐山一個警示
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟那傢伙 我以為他又要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1102,706)}門的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.43,0:24:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有人在心情不好的時候吃冰的東西
